Run hotplug.sh as given below

$./hotplug.sh arg1 arg2

arg1: How many CPUs to hotplug
arg2: How many seconds to perform the test

Eg:
root@freescale-ls1043a:~# ./hotplug.sh 4 100
----------------- CPU hotplug test starting ---------------------
Making all CPUs online
stress: info: [3243] dispatching hogs: 16 cpu, 0 io, 0 vm, 0 hdd
Will do hotplug test for 100 seconds
